<Body>
	<Title>广西南梧二级路藤县特大交通事故 4死9伤</Title>
	<ReportTime type="absTime">2007-7-15</ReportTime>
	<Content>
    <Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e1" type="thoughtevent"><Participant sid="s1">中广网</Participant><Location lid="l1">梧州</Location><Time tid="t1" type="relTime">7月15日</Time><Denoter did="d1" type="statement">消息</Denoter></Event>（记者陈俊 梧州电台谢大明）</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e2"><Time tid="t2" type="relTime">7月14日18时20分</Time>，<Location lid="l2">广西南宁至梧州二级公路藤县塘步镇大罗村路段</Location>发生一起<Denoter did="d2" type="emergency">交通事故</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e3"><Object sid="s3">一辆货车</Object>与<Object sid="s3">一辆客车</Object><Denoter did="d3" type="action">相撞</Denoter></Event>，造成<Event eid="e4"><Participant sid="s4">4人</Participant><Time tid="t4" type="relTime">当场</Time><Denoter did="d4" type="stateChange">死亡</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e5"><Participant sid="s5">9人</Participant><Denoter did="d5" type="stateChange">受伤</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e6" type="thoughtevent">据<Participant sid="s6">交警</Participant>初步<Denoter did="d6"  type="statement">查明</Denoter></Event>，事发路段当时一场大雨刚过，<Event eid="e7">一辆车牌号为“陕E20931”的<Object sid="s7">货车</Object>由西往东方向<Denoter did="d7" type="action">行驶</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e8">一辆车牌号为“桂D31103”广州至藤县的<Object sid="s8">客车</Object>由东往西方向<Denoter did="d8" type="action">行驶</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e9"><Object sid="s9">两车</Object><Denoter did="d9"  type="operation">会车</Denoter></Event>时，<Event eid="e10"><Object sid="s10">货车</Object>突然一头<Denoter did="d10" type="action">撞向</Denoter>了<Object oid="o10">客车尾部</Object></Event>，<Event eid="e11"><Participant sid="s11">货车两司机</Participant><Time tid="t11" type="relTime">当场</Time><Denoter did="d11" type="stateChange">死亡</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e12"><Object sid="s12">车头</Object>严重<Denoter did="d12" type="stateChange">变形</Denoter>作废</Event>。</Sentence><Sentence>由于受撞击的强大作用力，<Event eid="e13">客车则有<Participant sid="s13">2人</Participant><Time tid="t13" type="relTime">当场</Time><Denoter did="d13" type="stateChange">死亡</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e14"><Participant sid="s14">9人</Participant><Denoter did="d14" type="stateChange">受伤</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e15"><Time tid="t15" type="relTime">随后</Time>，<Object sid="s15">客车</Object><Denoter did="d15" type="action">驶向</Denoter><Location lid="l15">公路左侧路边</Location></Event>。<Event eid="e16">幸亏<Object sid="s16">客车</Object>在<Location lid="l16">离高坎不到20厘米处</Location><Denoter did="d16" type="action">停</Denoter>了下来</Event>，才避免了更大的损失。</Sentence></Paragraph>
		<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e17"><Denoter did="d17" type="emergency">事故</Denoter>发生</Event>后，<Event eid="e18"><Participant sid="s18,s19">交通警察、消防官兵和医护人员</Participant>在<Time tid="t18" type="relTime">第一时间</Time><Denoter did="d18" type="movement">赶到</Denoter><Location lid="l18">现场</Location></Event><Event eid="e19"><Denoter did="d19" type="operation">处理</Denoter><Object oid="o19">事故</Object></Event>、<Event eid="e20"><Denoter did="d20" type="operation">抢救</Denoter><Participant oid="o20">伤员</Participant></Event>。<Event eid="e21">梧州市和藤县的<Participant sid="s21,s22,s23">领导</Participant>也<Denoter did="d21" type="movement">赶往</Denoter><Location lid="l21">现场</Location></Event><Event eid="e22"><Denoter did="d22" type="perception">了解</Denoter><Object oid="o22">情况</Object></Event>、<Event eid="e23"><Denoter did="d23" type="operation">组织</Denoter><Event eid="e24"><Denoter did="d24" type="operation">抢救</Denoter></Event>和<Event eid="e25"><Object oid="o25">事故</Object><Denoter did="d25" type="operation">处理</Denoter></Event><Object oid="o23">工作</Object></Event>，<Event eid="e26"><Time tid="t26" type="relTime">至21时20分</Time>，<Location lid="l26">这一路段</Location>恢复了<Denoter did="d26" type="stateChange">通车</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>
		<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e27"><Time tid="t27" type="relTime">目前</Time>，<Object oid="o27">事故</Object>还在进一步<Denoter did="d27" type="operation">调查处理</Denoter>中</Event>，伤员伤情稳定。</Sentence></Paragraph>
